{{Expand Slovene|Pod milim nebom|topic=culture|date=July 2012}} {{Infobox book | name =Pod milim nebom | title_orig = | translator = | image = | image_caption = | author = [[Desa Muck]] | illustrator = | cover_artist = | country = {{flag|Slovenia}} | language = [[Slovenian language|Slovenian]] | series = | subject = | genre = | publisher = | pub_date = | english_pub_date = | media_type = | pages = | isbn = | oclc = | dewey = | congress = | preceded_by = | followed_by = }} '''''Pod milim nebom''''' is a novel by [[Slovenia]]n author [[Desa Muck]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.svetizbesed.com/index.php?t=zgodba&i=91|title=Pod milim nebom|publisher=Svetizbesed.com|accessdate=19 July 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011091406/http://www.svetizbesed.com/index.php?t=zgodba&i=91|archivedate=11 October 2007|df=}}</ref> It was first published in 2009.
